cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.DS, cs.IT

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper is about describing and simulating internet routes.
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is also likely as the paper may discuss security implications of route tracing and simulation.
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a possibility as the paper may discuss the structure and properties of the internet graph.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper may discuss algorithms for generating artificial routes.
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a possibility as the paper may discuss information theoretic properties of internet routes.
